1
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:04,680
The final round of the regular season

2
00:01:04,719 --> 00:01:07,079
Both teams face a battle for honor

3
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:08,079
The match is underway

4
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:10,000
Suzhou Team attacks down the right

5
00:01:10,040 --> 00:01:11,200
A cross that doubles as a shot

6
00:01:11,319 --> 00:01:13,280
The ball finds the far corner

7
00:01:29,239 --> 00:01:30,719
Changzhou FC with successive passes

8
00:01:30,719 --> 00:01:31,920
Also attacking down the flank

9
00:01:31,959 --> 00:01:32,959
Making a run to the back post

10
00:01:32,959 --> 00:01:33,640
A header on goal

11
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:34,560
Goal!

12
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:36,519
Fans from both teams at the stadium

13
00:01:36,599 --> 00:01:38,560
Keep chanting and cheering

14
00:01:38,599 --> 00:01:40,120
To support their respective teams

15
00:02:06,439 --> 00:02:07,040
Suzhou Team

16
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,000
In the final moments

17
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,280
Who would have thought

18
00:02:09,439 --> 00:02:10,960
Suzhou Team, in the dying seconds

19
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:11,960
Finds the back of the net

20
00:02:12,039 --> 00:02:13,520
Absolutely incredible!

21
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,879
The referee's final whistle

22
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,360
The match is over

23
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,639
Congratulations to Suzhou Team

24
00:02:18,719 --> 00:02:20,599
In the final round of the regular season

25
00:02:20,719 --> 00:02:22,120
Coming from behind

26
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:23,080
To pull off a comeback win

27
00:02:23,319 --> 00:02:25,039
And thanks also to Changzhou FC

28
00:02:25,159 --> 00:02:25,879
In this match

29
00:02:25,919 --> 00:02:27,680
They also showed limitless potential

30
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,800
in their attacking play

31
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:48,879
This summer

32
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:51,039
Between Jiangsu's thirteen cities,

33
00:03:51,039 --> 00:03:52,400
The Jiangsu Super League

34
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:54,360
Has taken the nation by storm

35
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,520
From a game for fans

36
00:03:56,759 --> 00:03:57,800
To a game for everyone

37
00:03:58,319 --> 00:03:59,479
From Jiangsu's own Super League

38
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:00,879
To an internet-wide sensation

39
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:02,000
It scored a stunning goal

40
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:04,520
that everyone gets to be part of

41
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,680
And my hometown's Changzhou FC

42
00:04:06,919 --> 00:04:08,360
Eight rounds in, not a single goal

43
00:04:08,479 --> 00:04:09,439
Dead last in the standings

44
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,639
A textbook Thirteen-Nil

45
00:04:11,319 --> 00:04:12,360
The "Super" in Jiangsu Super League

46
00:04:12,639 --> 00:04:14,319
Stands for a super tough story to cover

47
00:04:14,919 --> 00:04:16,120
That was my very first impression

48
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:17,120
when I started reporting

49
00:04:18,639 --> 00:04:20,000
In front of my camera

50
00:04:20,279 --> 00:04:22,079
Li Xiaoyong, who runs a breakfast stall

51
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:24,079
Zhou Hang, an animal trainer at Dino Park

52
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,240
PE teacher Xie Zhiyang

53
00:04:26,879 --> 00:04:28,519
Engineer Lü Donglin

54
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,319
In their ordinary day jobs

55
00:04:30,639 --> 00:04:31,560
Working by day

56
00:04:31,759 --> 00:04:32,680
Training by night

57
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:34,480
Amateur players take the field

58
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,600
And become the leading stars

59
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,639
A city's honor

60
00:04:36,839 --> 00:04:38,439
Defended by everyday heroes

61
00:04:38,639 --> 00:04:39,560
This angle

62
00:04:39,759 --> 00:04:42,040
Struck a chord with the public first

63
00:04:42,879 --> 00:04:44,199
If we can't beat them with our feet

64
00:04:44,319 --> 00:04:44,959
Then we'll just

65
00:04:45,279 --> 00:04:46,319
Beat them with our wit

66
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:50,600
Before the match against Wuxi,

67
00:04:50,639 --> 00:04:51,959
This was the short video we released

68
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,160
Fearless

69
00:04:53,879 --> 00:04:54,800
Official narratives

70
00:04:54,839 --> 00:04:56,879
Resonating with grassroots voices

71
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:59,160
Rival cities teased Changzhou again,

72
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,279
Saying we lost so bad we became "| Zhou"

73
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,920
We took the joke and ran with it

74
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,680
Posting the stroke count of "Changzhou"

75
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:04,959
And responding in dialect

76
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:05,959
"Jie Gun"

77
00:05:06,519 --> 00:05:07,560
Meaning "awesome"

78
00:05:07,839 --> 00:05:09,240
Became Changzhou fans'

79
00:05:09,319 --> 00:05:11,560
Slogan on shirts and rallying cry

80
00:05:11,879 --> 00:05:13,240
In this Jiangsu Super League,

81
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:14,399
Our Nanjing team has stuck to

82
00:05:14,399 --> 00:05:15,199
The same old spirit of

83
00:05:15,199 --> 00:05:15,879
"Friendship first,

84
00:05:15,959 --> 00:05:17,759
Competition fourteenth"

85
00:05:17,839 --> 00:05:18,600
"Competition first,

86
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,800
Friendship fourteenth"

87
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,199
That was a stroke of genius

88
00:05:21,199 --> 00:05:22,040
From netizens in the comments

89
00:05:22,079 --> 00:05:23,040
So we brought in

90
00:05:23,279 --> 00:05:24,680
The Dino Sis IP

91
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:26,360
And Jiangsu's "Thirteen Warriors" culture

92
00:05:26,399 --> 00:05:27,319
And played on the meme again

93
00:05:27,759 --> 00:05:29,199
Everyone wants to be Brother Nan

94
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,839
Everyone loves Thirteen-Nil

95
00:05:31,319 --> 00:05:32,399
Even the byline

96
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:34,680
Was changed to "Dying to Score"

97
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,319
Regional culture

98
00:05:37,399 --> 00:05:38,600
is a goldmine for media outreach

99
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:39,279
Internet language

100
00:05:39,279 --> 00:05:41,360
can recode a city's self-confidence

101
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:42,720
This let us strike a golden goal

102
00:05:42,839 --> 00:05:43,680
where sports journalism

103
00:05:43,759 --> 00:05:46,000
empowers cultural tourism and consumption

104
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:48,560
But returning to the sport itself,

105
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:49,800
as a journalist,

106
00:05:49,959 --> 00:05:52,279
how do you report eight winless rounds?

107
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:55,120
The night Changzhou played Nanjing,

108
00:05:55,519 --> 00:05:56,360
torrential rain poured down

109
00:05:56,519 --> 00:05:57,920
and we were down 0-4

110
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:59,439
with no chance of victory.

111
00:05:59,839 --> 00:06:00,439
Li Xiaoyong

112
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:02,360
launched another crucial shot.

113
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,839
The ball hit the post,

114
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:04,920
and bounced back.

115
00:06:05,519 --> 00:06:06,680
The whole stadium groaned.

116
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,360
Assistant coach Yun Zheng

117
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:10,040
fell to his knees, head in his hands.

118
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,839
Rain and tears

119
00:06:11,839 --> 00:06:13,519
streamed down his cheeks.

120
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:15,639
That moment was caught on camera

121
00:06:15,839 --> 00:06:17,240
and became, in fans' hearts,

122
00:06:17,439 --> 00:06:18,800
the iconic moment of the year.

123
00:06:19,959 --> 00:06:21,519
That regret in the mud,

124
00:06:21,519 --> 00:06:22,199
that refusal to give in,

125
00:06:22,439 --> 00:06:24,399
isn't that a mirror of ourselves?

126
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:27,120
While shouting alongside everyone,

127
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,800
"Keep fighting!"

128
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,480
I raised my phone

129
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,720
and filmed this clip,

130
00:06:31,839 --> 00:06:32,879
which was reposted across platforms,

131
00:06:32,959 --> 00:06:33,920
drawing over 200 million views

132
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,240
and resonating with a massive audience.

133
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:37,120
In the face of adversity,

134
00:06:37,319 --> 00:06:39,759
do you keep fighting for the dream?

135
00:06:40,399 --> 00:06:41,079
That includes

136
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:43,160
us in the media convergence wave,

137
00:06:43,439 --> 00:06:44,879
constantly struggling to stay afloat.

138
00:06:45,639 --> 00:06:46,399
Among 60 million daily posts...

139
00:06:46,399 --> 00:06:47,000
Hey folks,

140
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:47,879
usually,

141
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:49,800
it's Reporter Lü who supports us.

142
00:06:49,959 --> 00:06:50,480
Today,

143
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:51,959
let's all repost together

144
00:06:52,319 --> 00:06:53,560
to support Reporter Lü.

145
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,800
Testing the waters of social media

146
00:06:54,839 --> 00:06:55,879
as traditional TV journalists,

147
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:56,639
this time

148
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,240
we broke media boundaries,

149
00:06:58,439 --> 00:06:59,639
opened up our content platform,

150
00:06:59,879 --> 00:07:01,079
and co-created with netizens.

151
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:03,600
Under the Jiangsu Super League topic,

152
00:07:03,759 --> 00:07:05,399
amateur-shot short videos accounted for

153
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:07,120
over 70 percent.

154
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,720
Even 80-year-old grandmas

155
00:07:08,759 --> 00:07:09,360
were scrolling through them.

156
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,360
Xuzhou vs. Suqian, a Chu-Han clash,

157
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:12,319
stretchers came onto the pitch

158
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,600
and carried off six players.

159
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,360
That gave us

160
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:16,720
the inspiration to issue Xuzhou

161
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:19,040
an ironic "gentle challenge".

162
00:07:20,079 --> 00:07:22,040
Locals even used tactical commentary

163
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:23,439
to dub videos of dried radish fried rice.

164
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:24,439
The food angle

165
00:07:24,519 --> 00:07:25,319
became our way

166
00:07:25,519 --> 00:07:26,959
of giving fans around the world

167
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:28,240
a taste of hometown warmth.

168
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:30,720
From social media

169
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:32,079
to official media at home and abroad,

170
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,839
Changzhou's multi-layered,

171
00:07:33,839 --> 00:07:35,000
convergent media coverage

172
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:37,040
surpassed 10 billion views.

173
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:39,160
The Jiangsu Super League hit number one

174
00:07:39,199 --> 00:07:40,120
on trending searches five times,

175
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:42,199
with Changzhou taking four of those.

176
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,759
This screamer of breakthrough thinking

177
00:07:44,759 --> 00:07:46,000
made me understand even more:

178
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:48,160
from aloof exclusives

179
00:07:48,319 --> 00:07:49,720
to staying down-to-earth,

180
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:50,920
the people's football

181
00:07:50,959 --> 00:07:53,360
calls for the people's voice and empathy.

182
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:55,000
And value-driven leadership

183
00:07:55,439 --> 00:07:57,800
reshaped the win-or-lose narrative.

184
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,199
Round nine,

185
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,759
Changzhou versus Zhenjiang,

186
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:03,160
in the 86th minute,

187
00:08:03,519 --> 00:08:05,399
Li Xiaoyong took a pass from Zhou Hang

188
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,360
and slotted it home.

189
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,240
Quick, quick, quick!

190
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:09,360
Hit like, hit like!

191
00:08:09,439 --> 00:08:10,240
Hurry, give me a like!

192
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:10,800
Done, done!

193
00:08:10,879 --> 00:08:11,360
Like it like crazy!

194
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:14,360
Did you guys like it?

195
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:15,120
Yes, we did.

196
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:18,040
But the team leader smiled and said,

197
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,399
"Not bad at all."

198
00:08:19,399 --> 00:08:20,519
"Don't cry, Thirteen-Nil."

199
00:08:20,639 --> 00:08:22,240
"Tears are pearls."

200
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:24,079
"But thanks for capturing it."

201
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:24,879
"Let me give you some likes."

202
00:08:25,319 --> 00:08:26,360
Like, like, like.

203
00:08:26,399 --> 00:08:27,399
They all felt

204
00:08:27,519 --> 00:08:28,800
this was praise.

205
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,480
Isn't this recognition

206
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:31,480
also

207
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,320
an honor to our

208
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,440
journalistic spirit?

209
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:35,879
I just wanted to capture these

210
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,080
handsome dads

211
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:38,039
and stubborn husbands,

212
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:39,399
to show them to more people.

213
00:08:39,759 --> 00:08:40,480
To show how

214
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:41,840
they fight for what they love.

215
00:08:41,879 --> 00:08:43,120
Beyond winning and losing,

216
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:45,960
beyond football itself.

217
00:08:47,639 --> 00:08:48,519
Netizens commented,

218
00:08:49,639 --> 00:08:51,120
"We're all just ordinary people,"

219
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,440
"willing to stand by our dreams."

220
00:08:54,519 --> 00:08:55,559
Through countless hardships,

221
00:08:55,919 --> 00:08:57,080
through every possible effort,

222
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,600
through tireless calls,

223
00:08:58,799 --> 00:09:01,600
it became millions of echoes.

224
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:03,799
The Jiangsu Super League

225
00:09:04,039 --> 00:09:05,919
is just a small league in China,

226
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:08,320
and Changzhou FC is a team

227
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:10,039
near the bottom of that league.

228
00:09:10,559 --> 00:09:12,600
But never giving up in adversity,

229
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:13,960
fighting on through wind and rain,

230
00:09:14,279 --> 00:09:15,440
they let us feel, on a small field,

231
00:09:15,559 --> 00:09:16,440
the pulse

232
00:09:16,559 --> 00:09:19,320
of a striving, modern China.

233
00:09:19,639 --> 00:09:20,600
And in the mutual journey

234
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:22,360
between media and audience,

235
00:09:22,639 --> 00:09:23,840
they turned a viral legend

236
00:09:23,919 --> 00:09:26,519
into a transfer of positive energy.

237
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,080
While filming with the team,

238
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:31,240
the leader gave me this jersey.

239
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:31,919
He said,

240
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,879
"Eleven players on the field,"

241
00:09:33,919 --> 00:09:34,960
"plus the coach, plus you."

242
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,279
"Come on, Thirteen-Nil."

243
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,840
And on the track of media convergence,

244
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:39,879
Thirteen-Nil

245
00:09:40,279 --> 00:09:41,720
will give it everything she's got,

246
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,240
and bravely press forward.

247
00:09:43,919 --> 00:09:45,039
Let's all,

248
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,360
keep going!

249
00:10:04,879 --> 00:10:05,480
Coach Chang,

250
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:06,799
I've made up my mind.

251
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:12,080
Changzhou FC needs new blood next year.

252
00:10:12,919 --> 00:10:13,919
A whole new batch of players.

253
00:10:15,159 --> 00:10:16,600
Hope they score some good results.

254
00:10:17,919 --> 00:10:19,480
What are your plans now?

255
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:22,399
Haven't figured it out.

256
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:26,200
I'm not good with words.

257
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,000
I don't know what to do.

258
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,200
Take your time to think it through.

259
00:10:32,639 --> 00:10:33,279
Otherwise,

260
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,039
just be like me

261
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:36,519
and switch to coaching.

262
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,720
Whatever you decide to do,

263
00:10:39,919 --> 00:10:40,879
I'll always support you.

264
00:10:44,399 --> 00:10:45,759
Can I be a good coach?

265
00:10:48,679 --> 00:10:51,039
A player needs grit

266
00:10:51,399 --> 00:10:51,919
and drive.

267
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:53,639
A coach

268
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,240
needs patience

269
00:10:55,279 --> 00:10:56,080
and dedication.

270
00:10:57,279 --> 00:10:59,039
I watched you grow up.

271
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,679
Solid character and sense of duty.

272
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,039
I have faith in you.

273
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:11,919
Mister! Mister!

274
00:11:11,919 --> 00:11:13,159
Kick the ball back!

275
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,480
Thanks, Mister! Thanks!

276
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:42,159
Look,

277
00:11:42,399 --> 00:11:43,000
what I bought.

278
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:44,759
That's a lot.

279
00:11:45,799 --> 00:11:47,039
I'm gonna make my specialty.

280
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:48,360
Brother Chang's home-style cooking.

281
00:11:48,639 --> 00:11:50,360
Gonna treat Yan to a good meal.

282
00:11:50,799 --> 00:11:51,600
You sure you can pull it off?

283
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:02,799
This season of the Jiangsu Super League

284
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:04,200
may have ended just like that,

285
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:06,919
but at least we

286
00:13:06,919 --> 00:13:08,279
still get to play ball together.

287
00:13:09,399 --> 00:13:10,320
I'm pretty content with that.

288
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:11,960
You said it.

289
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:13,720
Before, it was just work every day,

290
00:13:13,799 --> 00:13:14,919
